  "body": "### Description\n\nWould be nice if the OIDC client would support the following:\r\n\r\nThe OIDC client can be configured to perform a single retry on requests that return status code 401 (Forbidden). When the option flag: refreshTokenOnForbidden is set to true, then the client will perform a new token request retry the original request before passing the response to the user.\r\n\r\nSee https://vertx.io/docs/vertx-web-client/java/#_oauth2_security option refreshTokenOnForbidden\r\n\r\n\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
